      "end": 16.071,
      "duration": 10.538,
      "caption": "先学平方根、算术平方根和立方根，再认识无理数和实数。"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "scene": 1,
      "start": 16.071,
      "end": 21.077,
      "duration": 5.006,
      "caption": "主线：想逆运算，分清根号，估位置，再比较。"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "scene": 2,
      "start": 21.497,
      "end": 28.951,
      "duration": 7.455,
      "caption": "求平方根，要反问：什么数平方后等于它。"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "scene": 2,
      "start": 28.951,
      "end": 37.105,
      "duration": 8.154,
      "caption": "7² = 49，(-7)² = 49，所以 49 的平方根是 ±7。"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "scene": 2,
      "start": 37.105,
      "end": 42.23,
      "duration": 5.125,
      "caption": "算术平方根只取非负值，√49 = 7。"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "scene": 2,
      "start": 42.23,
      "end": 46.423,
      "duration": 4.193,
      "caption": "负数没有平方根，0 的平方根还是 0。"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "scene": 3,
      "start": 46.843,
      "end": 49.816,
      "duration": 2.973,
      "caption": "x³ = a 时，x 叫做 a 的立方根，记作 ∛a。"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "scene": 3,
      "start": 49.816,
      "end": 53.904,
      "duration": 4.088,
      "caption": "负数也有立方根，∛(-27) = -3。"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "scene": 3,
      "start": 53.904,
      "end": 56.226,
      "duration": 2.322,
      "caption": "先看题目问平方根、算术平方根，还是立方根。"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "scene": 4,
      "start": 56.646,
      "end": 60.119,
      "duration": 3.473,
      "caption": "有限小数和无限循环小数是有理数。"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "scene": 4,
      "start": 60.119,
      "end": 61.242,
      "duration": 1.124,
      "caption": "有理数和无理数统称实数。"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "scene": 4,
      "start": 61.242,
      "end": 65.124,
      "duration": 3.881,
      "caption": "√9 = 3 是有理数，不是所有带根号的数都是无理数。"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "scene": 5,
      "start": 65.544,
      "end": 74.164,
      "duration": 8.62,
      "caption": "实数都能在数轴上找到对应点。"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "scene": 5,
      "start": 74.164,
      "end": 80.956,
      "duration": 6.792,
      "caption": "2² < 5 < 3²，所以 2 < √5 < 3。"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "scene": 5,
      "start": 80.956,
      "end": 89.576,
      "duration": 8.62,
      "caption": "继续比较 2.2²、2.3²，可以把位置估得更准。"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "scene": 6,
      "start": 89.996,
      "end": 95.911,
      "duration": 5.915,
      "caption": "例题一：求 64 的算术平方根、64 的平方根和 -27 的立方根。"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "scene": 6,
      "start": 95.911,
      "end": 101.825,
      "duration": 5.915,
      "caption": "64 的算术平方根是 8。"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "scene": 6,
      "start": 101.825,
      "end": 105.768,
      "duration": 3.943,
      "caption": "64 的平方根是 ±8。"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "scene": 6,
      "start": 105.768,
      "end": 110.608,
      "duration": 4.839,
      "caption": "-27 的立方根是 -3。"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "scene": 7,
      "start": 111.028,
      "end": 115.226,
      "duration": 4.199,
      "caption": "例题二：比较 √10 与 3.1 的大小。"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "scene": 7,
      "start": 115.226,
      "end": 124.149,
      "duration": 8.922,
      "caption": "3² = 9，4² = 16，所以 3 < √10 < 4。"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "scene": 7,
      "start": 124.149,
      "end": 135.958,
      "duration": 11.809,
      "caption": "3.1² = 9.61，3.2² = 10.24，所以 3.1 < √10 < 3.2。"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "scene": 7,
      "start": 135.958,
      "end": 138.582,
      "duration": 2.624,
      "caption": "因此 √10 > 3.1。"
    },
    {
